              "settings": {
                "title": "<body>\n\n\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n  <title>Glassmorphism Hero Section</title>\n  <style>\n    * {\n      margin: 0;\n      padding: 0;\n      box-sizing: border-box;\n    }\n\n    #shopify-block-AWjR6SWpGanltc0ZoR__text_block_Fpp6KU .hero-section {\n      background: url('https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0634/8239/6854/files/Diamond_Information_page_1.png?v=1748934327') no-repeat center center/cover;\n      height: 600px;\n      display: flex;\n      align-items: center;\n      padding: 0 5%;\n      position: relative;\n       justify-content: flex-end;\n    }\n\n    #shopify-block-AWjR6SWpGanltc0ZoR__text_block_Fpp6KU .glass-container {\n      max-width: 520px;\n      padding: 20px 25px;\n      border-radius: 20px;\n      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);\n      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);\n      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);\n      box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);\n      color: white;\n      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25);\n         text-align: center;\n    }\n\n    #shopify-block-AWjR6SWpGanltc0ZoR__text_block_Fpp6KU .glass-container h1 {\n     font-size: 36px;\n    margin-bottom: 12px;\n    text-align: center;\n    color: white;\n    }\n\n    #shopify-block-AWjR6SWpGanltc0ZoR__text_block_Fpp6KU .glass-container p {\n      font-size: 0.95rem;\n      line-height: 1.5;\n      color: #eee;\n      text-align: center;\n      font-family: mickir;\n     padding: 10px 0px\n    }\n    \n    #shopify-block-AWjR6SWpGanltc0ZoR__text_block_Fpp6KU .glass-container button{\n\npadding: 8px 16px;\nbackground-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);\n    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);\n    color: white;\n    border-radius: 20px;\n    cursor: pointer;\n    font-size: 0.9rem;\n    backdrop-filter: blur(4px);\n    transition: background 0.3s;\n    font-family: mickir;\n}\n\n    @media (max-width: 768px) {\n     #shopify-block-AWjR6SWpGanltc0ZoR__text_block_Fpp6KU .hero-section {\n        padding: 20px;\n        justify-content: center;\n        text-align: center;\n      }\n     #shopify-block-AWjR6SWpGanltc0ZoR__text_block_Fpp6KU .glass-container h1 {\n     font-size: 28px;\n    margin-bottom: 12px;\n    text-align: center;\n    color: white;\n    }\n     #shopify-block-AWjR6SWpGanltc0ZoR__text_block_Fpp6KU .glass-container {\n        width: 100%;\n      }\n    #shopify-block-AWjR6SWpGanltc0ZoR__text_block_Fpp6KU .hero-section {\n        background: url('https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0634/8239/6854/files/Diamond_Information_page_1.png?v=1748934327') no-repeat center center / auto;\n        height: 850px;\n        display: flex;\n        vertical-align: top;\n        align-items: flex-start;\n        padding: 0 5%;\n        position: relative;\n        padding-top: 30px;\n    }    \n#shopify-block-AWjR6SWpGanltc0ZoR__text_block_Fpp6KU .glass-container button {\n    padding: 8px 16px;\n    background-color: rgb(255 255 255 / 100%) !important;\n    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);\n    color: #28365a !important;\n    border-radius: 20px;\n    cursor: pointer;\n    font-size: 0.9rem;\n    backdrop-filter: blur(4px);\n    transition: background 0.3s;\n    font-family: mickir;\n}\n}\n  </style>\n\n\n\n  <section class=\"hero-section\">\n    <div class=\"glass-container\">\n      <h1>Diamond Cut</h1>\n      <p>The cut of a diamond determines how well it interacts with light affecting its brilliance (brightness), fire (rainbow dispersion), and scintillation (sparkle). While other qualities matter, nothing influences a diamond's beauty more than its cut quality. \n\n<br><br>A well-cut diamond is precisely shaped and proportioned to maximize light performance. When light enters an expertly cut diamond, it reflects from facet to facet and returns through the top, creating that captivating sparkle. In contrast, poorly cut diamonds allow light to escape through the sides or bottom, resulting in a dull, lifeless appearance. Cut quality scales typically range from Excellent to Poor, with the top grades representing optimal proportions that achieve maximum light return.</p>\n     <button><a href=\"https://vaama.co/collections/blush-collection\">Explore now</a></button>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n\n</body>",
